    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a great source for parts? This vehicle is priced to sell and ready for someone with a vision! While it needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for a dedicated DIYer or mechanic looking for their next challenge. Grab this bargain today and start your next big project!",
